{"tid":593684,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"投資的士牌的好處正在消失","createTime":"2018-03-15T07:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T09:25:43.000Z","uid":70274,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0bf36d5304d9e313a84696f101d2fb9da2ec6c","tid":593684,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"中環街市<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近交通工具認真多事，巴士司機罷工之後，就到的士司機慢駛抗爭，話要自決業界命運。<br />\n的士牌投資，一般年租金回報約4.5厘，算叫跑贏物業租金，然而回報背後的基本盤，正在慢慢消失：<br />\n「一口價」的士以及Uber的出現，間接影響司機承租能力<br />\n政府或對Uber等平台放寬<br />\n電子支付或令部份司機不能一邊拿綜援、一邊開的士<br />\n人口老化，僧多粥少<br />\n多年前香港司機好客的印象，已經一去不回<br />\n以前比較低調的投資，如今卻太多負面新聞<br />\n業界搞大慢駛都咁少人嚮應，變相減少了與政府談「專營」的籌碼<br />\n有車主透露，電動的士因為太煩無人租，被逼自己揸返<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n聽業內人士說，的士牌投資背後，有賴每天司機強勁的現金流，加上的士牌供應有限，造就買賣套現極快；但如果前線生意難做，難保減少人進入市場，最終「車主」無人流轉，而一班近年才進入的士投資市場的醫生、會計師等專業人士，就會成為輸家了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s2.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/b6D9Lb6sXsUhFSPREsGyEA--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3ZnBhZ2U7dz00ODA7cT03NTtzbT0x/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/centralmarket.tumblr.com/2856318c2ae0e97ec43e29b9f0ecd4a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fb6D9Lb6sXsUhFSPREsGyEA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3ZnBhZ2U7dz00ODA7cT03NTtzbT0x%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fcentralmarket.tumblr.com%2F2856318c2ae0e97ec43e29b9f0ecd4a0&d=h%2FRcGADQT8xoQXdpAzTjmQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a12dbe94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s2.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/b6D9Lb6sXsUhFSPREsGyEA--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3ZnBhZ2U7dz00ODA7cT03NTtzbT0x/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/centralmarket.tumblr.com/2856318c2ae0e97ec43e29b9f0ecd4a0</a><br />\n<br />\n來源：hktex"},{"pid":"4dd3a606747a8629519dce5c1c1ea2c6cafea628","tid":593684,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"食屎啦班的士佬"},{"pid":"58e092c509f03a56a3607b63b3758e3bb41a3be5","tid":593684,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9 先會買"},{"pid":"ec1991a353897e14ec9f791f9c7a9a53c6ea25c6","tid":593684,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"一日收租860<br />\n聽講回報唔錯"},{"pid":"185f318201ef7565ac77161c2fb338784f351ebf","tid":593684,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以比個市場自由發展先<br />\n點解的士牌要咁貴<br />\n冇競爭，唔休做，態度越黎越差<br />\n<br />\n開放個市場，引入競爭，做唔掂/態度差果班自然淘態，的士錢又唔撚洗咁貴<br />\n<br />\n如果咁做，就算開放新平台（例如uber），其實都仲有好多人會搭的士，uber價都唔見得會平好多。但的士因爲有登記，比較安全自然多d人搭<br />\n<br />\n而家係班的士牌牌主做左既得利益者，所以咪搞到累鬥累囉"},{"pid":"9ec1c4d375a7392b8ebfb3a63529ccb40b5efdab","tid":593684,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec1991a353897e14ec9f791f9c7a9a53c6ea25c6","tid":593684,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"一日收租860<br />\n聽講回報唔錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"聽講轉手唔洗俾印花稅"},{"pid":"b568dfa2d5fc8152acf8634534b243c964280976","tid":593684,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"抵丫 一定升唔會跌架<br />\n依家跌就話ban uber"},{"pid":"4cecd91a993174ad183213e54c6844eab0f7d4ff","tid":593684,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ec1c4d375a7392b8ebfb3a63529ccb40b5efdab","tid":593684,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec1991a353897e14ec9f791f9c7a9a53c6ea25c6","tid":593684,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"一日收租860<br />\n聽講回報唔錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"聽講轉手唔洗俾印花稅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"係，最少政府無所謂既辣招<br />\n但唔係內行人未必熟個運作<br />\n如果真係投資都驚驚地"},{"pid":"bff12956c83dc57fb988d4db21f5cdd79c9e17de","tid":593684,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:38: